data.value: Idera SQL Discovery helps you find SQL Servers installed in your network. The tool can be used to locate unknown SQL Servers that have been deployed, as well as to test the visibility of known SQL Servers. The discoverability of SQL Servers is affected by industry security best practices which are intended to protect servers from unauthorized access. The number of SQL Servers discovered by this tool will be limited if such practices are implemented on the target systems.
